        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">Read our story</a>
      </div>
      <div class="why-values">
        {[
          { icon: "ðŸ“–", title: "Story-first", text: "Every concept lives inside a story. No lectures." },
          { icon: "ðŸŽ¯", title: "One big idea per book", text: "Focused. Memorable. Actually read to the end." },
